<FIRST>r a PM-Lite     06-08 0361</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Lite,0374</SECOND>
<HEAD>On the Light Side</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BOSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Larger than the average lobbyist, two cows called
on the Statehouse with a group of concerned dairy farmers who
demanded higher prices for milk in Massachusetts.
   Dairy cows Jersey and Simon Kat quietly chewed their cuds while
two dozen farmers and their supporters rallied on the Statehouse
steps Tuesday.
   The farmers said high land prices were pushing them out of
business and threatening the state's dwindling dairy industry. A
proposal in the state Legislature would increase milk prices 2 cents
per quart, and the money would be distributed back to state dairy
farmers.
   ``It's either pay now or pay more later,'' said Dave Patterson of
the 2,200-member Agri-Mark, New England's largest dairy cooperative.
``It's not a tax, it's a rate hike.''
   The farmers argue that at $2.12 per gallon on average, the price
of milk in Massachusetts is lower than the national average.
   According to the state agriculture department, there were 3,000
dairy farms in Massachusetts in 1960 and only 460 active farms
today. Production dropped from 800 million pounds of milk in 1985 to
about 470 million pounds last year.
</TEXT>
<DATELINE>MACON, Ga. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Some couples prefer non-traditional wedding
gifts, but a man planning to tie the knot Saturday revealed more
than his taste in presents when he appeared nude in the July issue
of Playgirl magazine.
   In an interview accompanying the photo spread, Benny Graham
called it ``a great wedding gift to ourselves.''
   Graham, 27, appears in the magazine as winner of the ``1989 Make
Your Boyfriend a Centerfold'' contest. He was entered in the
competition by his fiancee, Kristy French.
   Neither was eager to comment about the honor Wednesday.
   ``We're just kind of going crazy around here with the wedding
coming in a couple days,'' Graham said. ``I'd rather wait until
after the wedding to talk about it.
   In the Playgirl interview, Graham said he was ``a little nervous
about posing nude, but I got over it and then I couldn't wait to do
it.''
   Graham, now employed by a plumbing and heating company, formerly
was owner of a fitness center. His fiancee is a second-grade teacher.
</TEXT>
