activist who recently visited the United States.
   Baez beamed as she opened the concert with a song with the
refrain, ``Build a brand new world.'' She called for solidarity with
students in China whose pro-democracy campaign has been brutally
repressed.
   American singer Stevie Wonder and French singer Yves Montand gave
concerts in support of Solidarity before the elections.
