   ``Mark J. Fogarty &amp; Angela G. Grace, a boy, Atom Skyler Grace
Fogarty, born April 25 in Upland, Calif. Mother is an actress.
Father is in postproduction at Warner Bros.
   ``Grandmother Teri Fogarty is Snookie the Clown.''
