deposited in the nation's savings and loans in April, the government
says.
   The withdrawals were down from the record rate earlier this year
but still high.
   Meanwhile Wednesday, private analysts predicted further
improvements in the next several months now that interest rates have
stopped climbing.
</TEXT>
