<HEAD>New Shuttles: Maple Veneer, Imitation Marble Vanities</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Trump Shuttle, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here is Donald Trump's plan for refurbishing the
interiors of his Northeast shuttle's fleet of 21 Boeing 727s, as
explained by the property developer at a news conference Wednesday:
   _Interiors: Will be redone using burgundy and tan tones, with
chrome and maple wood veneer accents.
