   The stock market advanced slightly today,
extending its recent rally fueled by takeover news and rumors and
declining interest rates.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials rose 2.94 to 2,515.26 by
11 a.m. on Wall Street.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by about 4 to 3 in
